      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just getting so hard lately. the doctors say my legs won't get better and i can't even make my own tea without shaking. i see my daughter's face when she has to come over and clean up after me... she looks so tired. i hate being such a weight on everyone. i feel like i'm just taking up space that they could use for something better.",
